%N A133338 Number of combinatorial types of simplicial neighborly 4-polytopes with n vertices.
%C A133338 For one of the 556062 combinatorial types of polytopes with n=12 vertices, it is unknown if it has a geometric realization. - _Andrei Zabolotskii_, Apr 12 2026
%D A133338 B. Gruenbaum, Convex Polytopes, 2nd Edition, p. 129a.
